# Advanced Dashboard Features & CRUD Implementation Plan

This plan outlines the architecture for transforming the dashboard into a fully interactive management system with live data, pagination, full CRUD capabilities for Bookings and Vehicles, and realtime notifications.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Supabase Realtime**: To enable push notifications for new bookings and messages, we need to enable **Supabase Realtime** for the `bookings` and `messages` tables. I will provide the SQL snippet for this, as it must be executed in your Supabase SQL editor.
> - **Database Schema Updates**: We will be adding Insert/Update/Delete operations. Please ensure your Supabase RLS policies allow the admin to perform these operations, or confirm if RLS is currently disabled for testing.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Dashboard Overview Interactivity & Pagination
#### [MODIFY] [src/components/dashboard/OrderList.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/components/dashboard/OrderList.tsx)
- Integrate Shadcn `<Pagination />` components.
- Slice the `bookings` array from Redux based on a `currentPage` state to paginate the data table smoothly.
- Ensure empty states are pristine and use Shadcn icons.
#### [MODIFY] [src/components/dashboard/StatisticCard.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/components/dashboard/StatisticCard.tsx)
- Ensure the stats cleanly update whenever the underlying Redux state changes (which we will sync with realtime updates).

### 2. Bookings Management (CRUD)
#### [MODIFY] [src/store/slices/bookingSlice.ts](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/store/slices/bookingSlice.ts)
- Add `createBooking`, `updateBooking`, and `deleteBooking` async thunks interfacing with Supabase.
#### [MODIFY] [src/app/dashboard/bookings/page.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/app/dashboard/bookings/page.tsx)
- Add "Create New Booking" Button opening `/dashboard/bookings/add`.
- Add an action menu (DropdownMenu) to each row with: "View Details", "Edit", "Accept/Refuse" (Quick status toggle between pending/confirmed/cancelled).
#### [NEW] `src/app/dashboard/bookings/add/page.tsx`
- Shadcn form for manual admin booking entry.
#### [NEW] `src/app/dashboard/bookings/[id]/page.tsx`
- Detailed read-only view of a booking's complete information.
#### [NEW] `src/app/dashboard/bookings/[id]/edit/page.tsx`
- Edit form for modifying dates, assigned car, or customer info. Includes a red "Delete Booking" Destructive Button.

### 3. Vehicles Management (CRUD)
#### [MODIFY] [src/store/slices/carsSlice.ts](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/store/slices/carsSlice.ts)
- Add `createCar`, `updateCar`, and `deleteCar` async thunks interfacing with Supabase.
#### [MODIFY] [src/app/dashboard/vehicles/all/page.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/app/dashboard/vehicles/all/page.tsx)
- Add actions column with "View Details", "Edit", and "Delete".
#### [NEW] `src/app/dashboard/vehicles/[id]/page.tsx`
- Premium details view of the vehicle, showing its image, specs, and current rental status.
#### [NEW] `src/app/dashboard/vehicles/[id]/edit/page.tsx`
- Form for editing car attributes. Includes a "Delete Vehicle" Destructive Button.
#### [MODIFY] [src/app/dashboard/vehicles/add/page.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/app/dashboard/vehicles/add/page.tsx)
- Wire the existing UI mockup to the `createCar` Redux thunk.

### 4. Real-time Notifications Setup
#### [MODIFY] [src/app/dashboard/layout.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/app/dashboard/layout.tsx) (or a new `NotificationManager.tsx` component)
- We will add the Shadcn `Toaster` component (using `sonner`).
- Implement a `useEffect` hook that creates a Supabase Realtime channel listening to `INSERT` events on the `messages` and `bookings` tables.
- When a guest submits the contact form or books a car on the public site, the admin dashboard will instantly pop a Toast notification ("New Booking received!" or "New Message received!").

## Verification Plan

### Automated/Build Checks
- Run `npm run build` after all dynamic `[id]` routes are created to ensure Next.js dynamic routing is correctly typed and bug-free.

### Manual Testing Protocol
1. **Pagination**: Create 15+ dummy bookings and verify [OrderList](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/dashboard%20ui/src/app/components/OrderList.tsx#32-112) paginates them (e.g., 5 per page).
2. **Bookings CRUD**: Manually Add a booking -> Verify it appears -> Accept it -> Edit it -> Delete it. Verify the Redux state updates without needing a page refresh.
3. **Vehicles CRUD**: Manually Add a car -> View Details -> Edit -> Delete.
4. **Notifications**: Open the Dashboard in one window, and the Guest Landing Page in another. Submit a booking/message on the guest page and watch for the instant Notification popup in the Dashboard window.
